PrecisAppointment of DAVID ADAM as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Panama; GERALD K. CAMPBELL as High Commissioner for Canada in the People's Republic of Bangladesh; RONALD DAVIDSON as Consul General of Canada at Sao Paulo (Federative Republic of Brazil); MICHEL DUVAL as Ambassador of Canada to the Lebanese Republic; JAMES FEIR as Consul General of Canada at Guangzhou (People's Republic of China); JAMES HILL as Consul General of Canada at Rio de Janeiro (Federative Republic of Brazil); JEREMY K.B. KINSMAN as Ambassador of Canada to the European Union; RICHARD LECOQ as Ambassador of Canada to the Socialist Republic of Vietnam; ROSALINE MURRAY as Ambassador of Canada to the Federal Democratic Republic of Ethiopia; and PHILIP SOMERVILLE as Ambassador of Canada to the Hellenic Republic.
